description.p:
A first aspect of the present invention provides an extendable cushion assembly, comprising:
A cushion which is movable between an extended state and a retracted state; and
A base upon which the cushion is removably coupled;
Wherein the base is movable between an extended state and a retracted state;
Wherein when the cushion is coupled to the base, when the base adopts the extended state or the retracted state the cushion is configured to adopt the extended or the retracted state respectively.
